      "title": "Navy arrests 54 on leaving for Australia",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy arrested 54 persons aboard a multi-day trawler bound for Australia off the coast of Batticaloa yesterday (26) morning.",
        "The Navy says that the illegal immigrants are being brought ashore."
